rows.label: qev041313_MSG0001
rows.name:
I feel my Ovah surge and dance at the sight of a
xiphias. What a wondrous Miralife Card.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041313_MSG0002
rows.name:
I picked up a Miralife Card in the park. It is yellowish
gold in color and bears an image of a nopopotamus.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041313_MSG0003
rows.name:
While pretty, it holds no meaning for meâ€”but I would
gladly display a xiphias card in my home![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041313_MSG0004
rows.name:
If you have any desire for this gold card,
I would welcome a trade.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041313_MSG0007
rows.name:
What do you say? Will you trade this gold
nopopotamus card for your xiphias card?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041313_MSG0008
rows.name:
My Ovah trembles with delight. It seems this xiphias
card was the proper match for me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041313_MSG0009
rows.name:
This gold nopopotamus card is yours.
Perhaps someone awaits it as I have awaited mine.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041313_MSG0010
rows.name:
Will you not reconsider? I am certain that I require
your xiphias card, and that you need this gold
one in turn.[ST:wait ]
